         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.225-2</ph> Buy American Certificate.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3401e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed
in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="25.1101.dita#FAR_25_1101"
                     base="i1090819"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">25.1101</xref>(a)(2)</ph>, insert
the following provision:</p>
         <p id="d3401e15"
            rev="FAC 2021-04 January 19, 2021"
            outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps"
            class="- topic/p "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2019-016?>Buy American Certificate (May 2014)<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 52.225-2 by—
a.  Revising the date of the provision ?></p>
         <ol id="d3361e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3401e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3401e26">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <ph rev="FAC 2021-04 January 19, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2019-016?>The Offeror certifies that
each end product, except those listed in paragraph (b) of this provision,
is a domestic end product.<?FM MARKER [Why] a.  Revising the date of the provision and paragraphs (a) and (b);?></ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3401e34">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <ph rev="FAC 2021-04 January 19, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">The Offeror shall
list as foreign end products those end products manufactured in
the United States that do not qualify as domestic end products.</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3401e40">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        <ph rev="FAC 2021-04 January 19, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">The terms "domestic
end product," "end product," and "foreign end product" are defined
in the clause of this solicitation entitled "Buy American-Supplies."</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
